{"3989890": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Shadow Island: Part I 🔞", "steam_appid": 3989890, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3989890/extras/d50dc5e62b61d4af0b096fe9143aa668.avif?t=1763125341\" width=86 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3989890/extras/54f774bc8eae978185aa97ebef3dabe2.avif?t=1763125341\" width=500 height=253 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Shadow Island: Part I</strong> tells the first half of a two-part, story-driven adventure that blends point-and-click exploration with branching choices.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">After surviving a shipwreck, you awaken on a mysterious island and set out to find your missing companion, Beatrice. As time passes, you will face dangers that stir in the dark, <strong>encounter alluring women</strong>, and uncover the first layers of the island’s hidden truths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Every feature, scene, and relationship you see here is part of <strong>Part I.</strong> The choices you make, and the bonds you form with the people you meet, will shape your path and carry into <strong>Part II</strong>, where the mystery of <strong>Shadow Island</strong> will reach its conclusion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Will you hold on to your purpose, or lose yourself before the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3989890/extras/f555e4aa820691d085a92ee47